	<key>readme</key>
	<string>## Functionality
Search and explore AI models on OpenRouter.

## Usage:
- Type `or &lt;query&gt;` to search models
- &lt;kbd&gt;⇥&lt;/kbd&gt; (Tab) on a result to see provider details
- &lt;kbd&gt;⏎&lt;/kbd&gt; (Enter) to open the model page on OpenRouter
- &lt;kbd&gt;⌘⏎&lt;/kbd&gt;: Open HuggingFace page (in detail view)
- &lt;kbd&gt;⌥⏎&lt;/kbd&gt;: Copy model ID to clipboard
- Type `orc` to clear all cache

## Configuration:
Set `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` (from `openrouter.ai/keys`) to enable latency and throughput data for providers.</string>
